title: What Should We Purchase Next?
body:
A) Place a bid on upcoming Nouns DAO releases. (Place a bid until one Nouns DAO NFT is successfully bought OR until another vote halts bidding.)
B) Purchase a floor CyberKongz Genesis and keep it in the DAO’s wallet to accumulate $BANANA until Fractional updates its functions to allow the collection/distribution of tokens. Every Friday, swap $BANANA for ETH and put that ETH back into the DAO’s ETH wallet to fund future purchases. Upon Fractional's update, fractionalize the CyberKongz NFT.
C) Purchase an XCOPY 1/1 (Specific NFT to be voted on if this choice wins this vote.)
D) Purchase 1 Floor Crypto Punk.
E) Purchase 10 Floor Cool Cats.
